
@startuml
title NetChat — Component Diagram

skinparam componentStyle rectangle

package "NetChat" {
	[CLI\n(Console UI)] as CLI
	[Chat Core] as Core
	[Protocol\n(MessageCodec)] as Protocol
	[Transport\n(TCP)] as Transport
}

CLI --> Core : user input / output
Core --> Protocol : encode/decode
Core --> Transport : open/close, send/receive
Transport --> Protocol : raw bytes <-> lines

note right of Protocol
NDJSON (UTF-8) поверх TCP.
Каждое сообщение — JSON в одной строке.
end note

@enduml

